{"TopicId":206771,"ForumId":112,"TopicTitle":"Solar flares","CreatedByName":"jaf","CreatedById":219088,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-05T17:50:15Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"jaf","CreatedById":219088,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-05T17:50:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\ntbh i just randomly got the idea for solar flares, and maybe even a radiation system where if a solar flare hits your ship or a colony thats on a planet/moon it could knock out some equipment.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr maybe if your around an unstable star?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"jastrone","CreatedById":208489,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-05T20:16:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthats random and that is not good game design\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"jaf","CreatedById":219088,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-05T20:39:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224087079\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022206771\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221644092191\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022208489\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022jastrone\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n20 minutes ago, jastrone said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthats random and that is not good game design\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nyour probably right considering i dindnt think this one through\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"LukewarmSpaghetti","CreatedById":219085,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-05T21:10:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI kind of like this idea. Say for example you are playing on hard mode; there is a risk of certain disasters happening while you play that require thinking and Kerbal solving to accomplish\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"adsii1970","CreatedById":89014,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-05T22:14:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224087079\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022206771\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221644092191\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022208489\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022jastrone\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, jastrone said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthats random and that is not good game design\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe one predictable factor about space exploration is there\u0027s no way we can predict everything that can happen!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSure, it\u0027s something that could be incorporated into the game, but only if the game had a \u0022hard as hell\u0022 mode - and I can assure you I\u0027d never play it!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224087126\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022206771\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221644095429\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022219085\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022LukewarmSpaghetti\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n56 minutes ago, LukewarmSpaghetti said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI kind of like this idea. Say for example you are playing on hard mode; there is a risk of certain disasters happening while you play that require thinking and Kerbal solving to accomplish\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn a way, I do, too. I\u0027d not want deadly solar flares, but mild ones that knock out communications for a few hours might make it more fun. It would also cause me to rethink communications satellite deployments more seriously than I do now. And also rethink some of my designs, too.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut - as I mentioned before, malfunctions in space are a part of the predictability of the unpredictable. It\u0027s the very essence of \u003Cem\u003Echaos\u003C/em\u003E theory in action - to expect the unexpected. And that\u0027s why one of my good forum buddies \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/106975-angel-125/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022106975\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/106975-angel-125/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Angel-125\u003C/a\u003E came up with this great (and at times, infuriating mod) that not only adds enjoyment and a bit of realism to the game, but has caused me to rage-quit a few times:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022106975\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed1171573601\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/164448-1122-baris-building-a-rocket-isnt-simple/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0026amp;comment=3149307\u0026amp;embedComment=3149307\u0026amp;embedDo=findComment#comment-3149307\u0022 style=\u0022height:297px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere are other mods out there that add other issues and challenges to your program, but I am not as familiar with them as I am with this one. Anyway, welcome to the forum, \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/219088-jaf/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022219088\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/219088-jaf/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@jaf\u003C/a\u003E and \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/208489-jastrone/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022208489\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/208489-jastrone/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@jastrone\u003C/a\u003E! When you get a chance, I hope you\u0027ll take the time to share some images of your craft in action. It\u0027s always great seeing what new folks to the game come up with. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0 \u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"awsumguy76801","CreatedById":212243,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-06T04:51:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224087025\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022206771\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221644083415\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022219088\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022jaf\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 hours ago, jaf said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ntbh i just randomly got the idea for solar flares, and maybe even a radiation system where if a solar flare hits your ship or a colony thats on a planet/moon it could knock out some equipment.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr maybe if your around an unstable star?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe that could be some hard mode feature that red dwarf stars get angry every so often and flare\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"jastrone","CreatedById":208489,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-06T09:54:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224087147\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022206771\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221644099253\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002289014\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022adsii1970\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 hours ago, adsii1970 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe one predictable factor about space exploration is there\u0027s no way we can predict everything that can happen!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nrelism does not equal fun.\u00A0 and therefore you shouldnt make games too realistic.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224087147\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022206771\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221644099253\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002289014\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022adsii1970\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 hours ago, adsii1970 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0022hard as hell\u0022 mode\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nits not hard or a challenge its just that you fail for something that wasent your fault\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"PlutoISaPlanet","CreatedById":206057,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-06T13:10:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224087025\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022206771\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221644083415\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022219088\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022jaf\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n19 hours ago, jaf said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ntbh i just randomly got the idea for solar flares, and maybe even a radiation system where if a solar flare hits your ship or a colony thats on a planet/moon it could knock out some equipment.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr maybe if your around an unstable star?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe do know radiation will play a factor with the engines, so it could have other factors.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"gussi111","CreatedById":212979,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-06T13:29:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224087462\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022206771\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221644153019\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022206057\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022PlutoISaPlanet\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n17 minutes ago, PlutoISaPlanet said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe do know radiation will play a factor with the engines\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhere did you hear that?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Maria Sirona","CreatedById":210882,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-06T13:35:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEh. It is something the player can\u0027t do anything about and will just frustrate people and will be no fun. I\u0027d say no to it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"PlutoISaPlanet","CreatedById":206057,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-06T13:54:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224087478\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022206771\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221644154185\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022212979\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022gussi111\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n22 minutes ago, gussi111 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhere did you hear that?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E radiation indicator. Also believe the devs mentioned it before.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheSameKerbal77","CreatedById":217455,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-09T21:39:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224087489\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022206771\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221644155667\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022206057\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022PlutoISaPlanet\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 2/6/2022 at 6:54 AM, PlutoISaPlanet said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E radiation indicator. Also believe the devs mentioned it before.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey did, no idea where tho...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Staticalliam7","CreatedById":216180,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-11T23:47:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI actually really like this idea\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"darthgently","CreatedById":204885,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-16T12:01:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224087429\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022206771\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221644141261\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022208489\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022jastrone\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 2/6/2022 at 4:54 AM, jastrone said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nrelism does not equal fun.\u00A0 and therefore you shouldnt make games too realistic.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nits not hard or a challenge its just that you fail for something that wasent your fault\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot really.\u00A0 Service bays and command parts could have optional shielding.\u00A0 Or the flare damage could be 10x more temporary if you have an engineer aboard.\u00A0 One can be, and a good player will be, somewhat prepared for the unpredictable.\u00A0 What is scary, and not fun, are those in real life who think nothing should be unpredictable and go into politics\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222022-02-16T13:11:30Z\u0022 title=\u002202/16/2022 01:11  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 16, 2022\u003C/time\u003E by darthgently\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}